eturn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pwb1665702747018.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pwb1665702747018.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pwb1665702747018.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pwb1665702747018\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Standalone On-Premises\n      Served License </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pwb1665702747018__on_premises_served_standalone_license_202845\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A standalone on-premises served license runs on a single machine and uses a local\n      license file. It is sometimes referred to as a <dfn class=\"term\">node-locked</dfn> license. It requires\n      no internet connection.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pwb1665702747018__p_d67037e1_d67038e1_d67039e1\">You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with\n         Uniface, which allows you to access the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://unifacebv.prod.sentinelcloud.com/customer/login\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sentinel EMS customer portal</a>, where you can lock your license to a specific\n         machine and obtain the actual license file.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pwb1665702747018__li_d29636e1_d29637e1_d29638e1\">To configure a standalone on-premises served\n            license, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uif1665702747088.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uif1665702747088.html\" title=\"To configure standalone on-premises licenses, you need to use the EMS portal and use the appropriate utility for your platform to get the locking criteria.\">Configuring Standalone On-Premises Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pwb1665702747018__li_d29639e1_d29640e1_d29641e1\">To return a standalone on-premises served license,\n            see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mko1665702747232.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mko1665702747232.html\" title=\"If you have a standalone on-premises served license that is no longer required, you can return it using the license revocation tool to disable the license file.\">Returning Standalone On-Premises Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531108\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Standalone On-Premises Served License Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Standalone On-Premises Served License A standalone on-premises served license runs on a single machine and uses a local license file. It is sometimes referred to as a node-locked license. It requires no internet connection. You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with Uniface, which allows you to access the Sentinel EMS customer portal , where you can lock your license to a specific machine and obtain the actual license file. To configure a standalone on-premises served license, see Configuring Standalone On-Premises Served Licenses . To return a standalone on-premises served license, see Returning Standalone On-Premises Served Licenses . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}